The invention relates to a high-tenacity mixing low pollution combustor discharging acid gas. The high-tenacity mixing low pollution combustor is characterized in that a conical opening for increasing the flowing rate of combustion-supporting air is arranged on the bottom of a combustion chamber, an end nozzle of a main gas burner in a central burner group is aligned to the small end of the conical opening; end air cyclones of an ammonia-containing acid gas burner and a sulphuric acid-containing gas burner in the central burner group extend into the big end of the conical opening to mix the acid gas with air in high tenacity; the central axis of the main gas burner is concentric with the central axis of the combustion chamber, and the central axes of the ammonia-containing acid gas burner and the sulphuric acid-containing gas burner positioned on the periphery of the main gas burner are concentric with the central axe of the main gas burner. The high tenacity mixing low pollution combustor discharging acid gas is capable of combusting various gases, has a wide regulation range, and utilizes combustion-supporting air at the normal temperature to guarantee the low temperature of the furnace wall and reduce the temperature of a fireproof liner of the combustion chamber under the cooling action of the combustion-supporting air, so that the invention can be safely and reliably operated at the working temperature lower than the allowed working temperature for a long time.
